		<div id="comment_body_64392422">It's not grammatically correct, but I'll confess that I used to do this. I did it because pluralizing something that's in all caps by following it with a lower case 's' looks weird, so I would add an apostrophe for the purpose of separating the two. Just to give them some space. It looks less weird.</div>
